Package: ggrcs
Type: Package
Title: A function to draw histograms and restricted cubic splines (RCS).
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Qiang LIU
Maintainer: Qiang LIU <dege857@163.com>
Description: You can use this function to easily draw a combined.histogram and restricted cubic spline.The function draws the graph through ggplot2.RCS fitting requires the use of the rcs function of the RMS package.Can fit cox regression, logistic regression .
License: GPL-3
Depends:
  R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
  rms,
  ggplot2,
  scales
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
